	<br>
	<div style="text-align:right;">
		AGUIAR, Matheus Lucas<sup>1</sup>; SILVA, Walan Robert da<sup>2</sup>; SCHEEREN, Eduardo Mendonça<sup>3</sup>		<BR>
		PIBIC		- Bolsa PUCPR-PIBIC		<BR>
